description:
Episode 254 - WHAT A TIME TO BE ALIVE! Great news everyone, we have an awesome chat to bring you this week with my new friend Cameron Boucher from Sorority Noise/Old Grey! We get in deep with talks about depression, musical naivety and spirituality. I love everything about this episode so join us, won’t you? Treat your Mom this holiday with AMAZING flowers, a free vase and candy with Bloom That!Who needs an excuse to eat sorbet? I don’t so eat up and enjoy Talenti!Use our Amazon Affiliate Code to support the show!
